CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Empro Group Inc., through its subsidiary, EMP Solution Sdn. Bhd., sells healthcare and beauty products in Malaysia and internationally. The company offers eyebrow pencils, skincare and antibacterial moisturizing mist products, surgical face masks, nitrile gloves, test kits, and black diamond eyeliners under the Empro, Premio, SpaceLift, and Mios brands. It sells its products through retails stores and online. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Shah Alam, Malaysia.
